\par }{\fs28\insrsid3024113\charrsid15666328 As much as possible, Patient should continue with the }{\fs28\insrsid10055121\charrsid15666328 normal lifestyle.}{\fs28\insrsid3024113\charrsid15666328 
\par }{\fs28\insrsid1324948\charrsid15666328 -}{\fs28\insrsid3024113\charrsid15666328 Should continue with his work or employment as normal.}{\fs28\insrsid10055121\charrsid15666328  }{\fs28\insrsid1324948\charrsid15666328 
